Uses of Package
xxl.core.indexStructures.builder

  • Packages that use xxl.core.indexStructures.builder 
    Package Description
    xxl.core.indexStructures
    Provides important index structures like B-trees, R-trees, M-trees and bulk-loading-algorithms.
    xxl.core.indexStructures.builder
    Providing builder classes for various index structures.
    xxl.core.indexStructures.builder.BPlusTree
    The builder class for BPlusTrees.
    xxl.core.util
    This package provides miscellaneous utility classes that don't belong strictly to an other xxl-package.
  • Classes in xxl.core.indexStructures.builder used by xxl.core.indexStructures 
    Class and Description
    IndexBuilder
    With the help of a concrete implementation of the abstract IndexBuilder class it is possible to easily generate index structures or restore them from a storage medium.
  • Classes in xxl.core.indexStructures.builder used by xxl.core.indexStructures.builder 
    Class and Description
    Builders.BPlusCreatorFacade
    This class simplifies the creation for BPlus indexes for various primitive or relational data types.
    Builders.BPlusLoaderFacade
    This is a helper class to provide a static from method which is for BPlusConfiguration loading.
    IndexBuilder
    With the help of a concrete implementation of the abstract IndexBuilder class it is possible to easily generate index structures or restore them from a storage medium.
    IndexConfiguration
    An abstract class for setting up requirements for a given index structure needed for a concrete IndexBuilder.
